---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Kindergarten (4K)">
  <section class="py-20 bg-surface-sand relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 relative z-10 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white border border-brand-red/30 text-xs font-semibold text-brand-red uppercase tracking-wide mb-6">
        Ages 4 Years
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Kindergarten (4K)</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-slate max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A comprehensive Junior Kindergarten program that prepares 4-year-olds for success in school and life.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-headings:font-heading prose-headings:text-brand-navy max-w-none text-text-ink leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Our Kindergarten (4K) program, formerly known as Junior Kindergarten, provides specialized care and education for 4-year-olds. We bridge the gap between early childhood and traditional elementary education by providing a responsive, play-based curriculum.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Curriculum</h2>
        <p>Our dedicated teaching staff plans integrated lessons focusing on key developmental areas:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Language Arts & Literacy:</strong> Building vocabulary, early reading skills, and love for storytelling.</li>
          <li><strong>Math:</strong> Foundational numeracy, shapes, patterns, and sorting.</li>
          <li><strong>Science & Social Studies:</strong> Exploring the world around them, community roles, and nature.</li>
          <li><strong>Creative Arts:</strong> Expression through music, movement, and visual arts.</li>
          <li><strong>Physical Education:</strong> Gross and fine motor skill development.</li>
          <li><strong>Play & Exploration:</strong> Open-ended discovery time critical for social-emotional growth.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-12 p-8 border-l-4 border-brand-sky bg-surface-sand text-brand-navy font-medium italic">
          "The leap my daughter made during her 4K year at Milestones was astounding. The curriculum is perfectly balanced between structured learning and imaginative play."
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <a href="/parents/enrollment" class="btn-primary no-underline text-white inline-flex">Enroll for Kindergarten</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
